race.comment: FORGOTTEN SPIRIT (6) competed in much richer contests in her first campaign before just missing the placings here when first-up from the spell. Should find this assignment much more to her liking and will play a major role in the finish. SPIRIT OF BARTY (10) saluted over this sprint journey when facing the starter for the first time and gets in on the minimum weight. Not to be underestimated. TORQUE TO BE SURE (1) wasn't disgraced in Group 1 company before the spell and is drawn to get all the favours from the inside alley. Watch for a strong run while fresh. SEAMS LOGICAL (7) next best out of the Webster camp.
